Post Part I:
This being my first week back to work after a month-long hiatus, I inevitably get the usual sort of questions people ask when you get back from a vacation:
&ldquo;Hey, where did you go?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Do you have anyÂ pasalubong?&rdquo; (souvenirs)
&ldquo;So, what did you do for one month?&rdquo;
I&rsquo;m amused by how very few people seem to get the fact that I didn&rsquo;t do &ldquo;anything&rdquo; in particular over the break.
